RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>수급자명</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="217" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{이용자성명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="218" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>보호자명 </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="219" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{보호자명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="219" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>관계</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="220" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{관계}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>본인은 #{센터명}와 방문요양 계약 시 아래의 내용에 대한 설명을 들었으며 이에 동의하고 확인합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>- 아   래 -</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>1. 급여계약을 체결할 때, 급여제공과 관련된 사항에 대해 설명을 듣고 계약서 부본을 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>2. 기관은 급여개시일 전에 수급자의 낙상, 욕창 위험도, 인지선별검사 및 욕구를 파악하고 그에 대한 설명을 하고 자료를 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>3. 기관은 급여개시일 전에 수급자의 개인별장기요양이용계획서, 위험도평가, 욕구사정을 기반으로 급여제공계획을 작성한 후 수급자(보호자)의 동의를 받았으며 급여제공계획서 부본을 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>4. 기관은 그 외 욕창예방, 낙상예방, 탈수예방, 배변도움, 관절구축예방, 치매예방, 감염예방, 노인인권보호에 대한 설명을 하고 자료를 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>5. 기관으로부터 급여제공범위 및 장기요양종사자의 인권(종사자에 대한 폭언,폭행,성희롱발생예방수칙, 상호존중수칙)에 대한 안내를 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>6. 기관으로부터 장기요양서비스 이용수칙에 대한 안내를 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="110" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"/></P><P ParaShape="99" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><FOOTER ApplyPageType="Both" SeriesNum="8"><PARALIST HasNumRef="false" HasTextRef="false" LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" TextHeight="1417" TextWidth="51026" VertAlign="Bottom"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P></PARALIST></FOOTER><CHAR>                                 </CHAR><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="3" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2033298619" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="88"><SIZE Height="2082" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="40165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="15826" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="1239" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="16457"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="99" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>수급자(또는 보호자) :</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="19806"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="188"><CHAR>#{이용자성명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="3902"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDi