CHAR>님의 기억력과 사고능력을 살펴보기 위한 질문들을 드리겠습니다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="113" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="106"><CHAR>생각나는 대로 최선을 다해 답변해 주시면 됩니다.”</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="50" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="13624" Protect="false" RowAddr="8" RowSpan="6" Width="3990"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="103" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>지남력</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="51" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="10770" Protect="false" RowAddr="8" RowSpan="5" Width="5297"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="103" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>시간</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="52" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="8" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="8" RowSpan="1" Width="35759"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="112" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>1. 오늘 날짜를 말씀해주세요.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="53" ColAddr="10" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="8" RowSpan="1" Width="5692"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="103" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="54" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="8" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="9" RowSpan="1" Width="35759"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="112" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR> (1) 올해는 몇 년도입니까?    [대상자 반응:                            ]</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="55" ColAddr="10" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="9" RowSpan="1" Width="5692"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="103" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>0     1</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="54" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="8" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="10" RowSpan="1" Width="35759"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="112" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR> (2) 지금을 몇 월입니까?      [대상자 반응:                            ]</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="55" ColAddr="10" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="10" RowSpan="1" Width="5692"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="103" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>0     1</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="54" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="8" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2154" Protect="false" RowAddr="11" RowSpan="1" Width="35759"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top