41"><CHAR>합      계</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="3505" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="14131"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR> 원</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="3505" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="14123"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="21" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR> 원</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="9"/></P><P ParaShape="73" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>○ 방문요양의 1회당 이용시간별 급여비용</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"/></P><P ParaShape="34" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="41"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"><TABLE BorderFill="81" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2015957190" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextFlow="BothSides" TextWrap="Square" ZOrder="84"><SIZE Height="24358" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="50444" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="false" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="164" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="82" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="71293" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="50444"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="86"><CHAR>개인정보 제공 및 활용 동의서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="40" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="63"/></P><P ParaShape="44" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>  당 기관은 이용 수급자에 대한 행정적인 업무와 수급자의 정신적, 신체적 욕구 및 특성 파악을 통해 보다 원활한 서비스 제공을 목적으로 개인정보를 수집 및 활용하겠습니다. 수집 및 활용의 범주는 다음과 같습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="16"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><TABLE BorderFill="83" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2015957191" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="85"><SIZE Height="35954" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="48858" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="84" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="35954" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="48858"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>1. 수집 및 이용목적</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>① 재가장기요양급여 제공 시 활용</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>② 타 기관 간의 서비스 연계 시 정보 제공 및 활용</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>③ 관련기관의 정보제공 요청 시 제공</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>④ 기타 장기요양계획, 수급자 욕구조사, 장기요양서비스 질 수준 향상 등에 활용</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>2. 수집항목</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>① 수급자 성명, 주민번호, 성별, 주소, 연락처 등 개인을 식별할 수 있는 기초정보</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>② 보호자 성명, 생년월일, 관계, 주소, 연락처</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>③ 장기요양인정번호, 장기요양등급 등 장기요양급여 관련 정보</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>④ 수급자의 지역연계 관련 정보</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>⑤ 관련기관의 정보제공 요청 시 필요한 정보</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>⑥ 기타 목적사업 수행에 필요한 정보</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"/></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>3. 보유 및 이용기간</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>관련 법령에 따라 장기요양급여 계약이 종료된 날까지 이용하며, 계약 종료된 날로부터 5년간 보유합니다. 제공한 개인정보 수집 및 이용에 대한 동의를 철회하는 경우, 또는 수집 및 이용목적이 달성되거나 보유 및 이용기간이 종료한 경우 이용자의 개인정보는 지체 없이 파기됩니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="16"><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="45" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>본 문건의 내용을 확인하고 숙지하였으며 개인정보 수집 및 활용에 동의합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="45" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="45" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137850119" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="89"><SIZE Height="1582" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="30543" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="15826" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="1239" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="30543"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{계약일}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="46" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="3" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="3"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137850120" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="90"><SIZE Height="10389" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="30391" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="6387" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="10825"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>주         소 :</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="2" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="6387" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="19566"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>#{이용자주소}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2001" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="10825"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>생 년   월 일 : </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="2" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2001" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="19566"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>#{이용자주민등록생년월일}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2001" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="10825"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>수급자(보호자) : </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2001" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="15870"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>#{이용자성명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2001" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="3696"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>(인)</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR>  </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="65"><CHAR/></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="65"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="86"><CHAR>계약내용 확인서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="34" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="4" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="3"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137850123" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextFlow="BothSides" TextWrap="Square" ZOrder="91"><SIZE Height="7010" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="48372" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="2138" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="false" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="718" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="213" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>안내일자</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="214" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{계약일}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="214" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>서비스시작일</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="215" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{서비스시작일}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="216" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>안내방법</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{안내방법}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>수급자명</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="217" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2337" Protect="false" RowAddr="1" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{이용자성명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="218" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>보호자명 </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="219" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{보호자명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="219" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="20" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>관계</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="220" ColAddr="3" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="2336" Protect="false" RowAddr="2" RowSpan="1" Width="12093"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>#{관계}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>본인은 #{센터명}와 방문요양 계약 시 아래의 내용에 대한 설명을 들었으며 이에 동의하고 확인합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>- 아   래 -</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>1. 급여계약을 체결할 때, 급여제공과 관련된 사항에 대해 설명을 듣고 계약서 부본을 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>2. 기관은 급여개시일 전에 수급자의 낙상, 욕창 위험도, 인지선별검사 및 욕구를 파악하고 그에 대한 설명을 하고 자료를 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>3. 기관은 급여개시일 전에 수급자의 개인별장기요양이용계획서, 위험도평가, 욕구사정을 기반으로 급여제공계획을 작성한 후 수급자(보호자)의 동의를 받았으며 급여제공계획서 부본을 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>4. 기관은 그 외 욕창예방, 낙상예방, 탈수예방, 배변도움, 관절구축예방, 치매예방, 감염예방, 노인인권보호에 대한 설명을 하고 자료를 제공하였습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>5. 기관으로부터 급여제공범위 및 장기요양종사자의 인권(종사자에 대한 폭언,폭행,성희롱발생예방수칙, 상호존중수칙)에 대한 안내를 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="100" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>6. 기관으로부터 장기요양서비스 이용수칙에 대한 안내를 받았습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="110" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"/></P><P ParaShape="99" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><FOOTER ApplyPageType="Both" SeriesNum="9"><PARALIST HasNumRef="false" HasTextRef="false" LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" TextWidth="51026" VertAlign="Bottom"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P></PARALIST></FOOTER><CHAR>                                 </CHAR><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="3" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2137850124" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="92"><SIZE Height="2082" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="40165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="15826" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="1239" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="16457"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="99" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>수급자(또는 보호자) :</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="19806"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="98" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="188"><CHAR>#{이용자성명}</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="78" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="3902"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>(인)</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="109" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"/></P><P ParaShape="36" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="37"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="86"><CHAR>재가전문요양보호사 안내</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="122"><CHAR>(수급자 제공용)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="6" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>어르신과 어르신 가정에 건강과 행복을 기원합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>저희 #{센터명}는 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>[보건복지부 지정 장기요양기관]으로서 어르신을 공경과 섬김으로 모시고 있습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>오늘부터 어르신을 섬길 직원에 대하여 안내드립니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>참고하시기 바라며 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="52"><CHAR>우리 직원일동은 변함없는 서비스가 되도록 항상 노력하겠습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><FOOTER ApplyPageType="Both" SeriesNum="17"><PARALIST HasNumRef="false" HasTextRef="false" LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" TextWidth="51026" VertAlign="Bottom"><P ParaShape="47" Style="13"><TEXT CharShape="32"/></P></PARALIST></FOOTER><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>- 안    내 -</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><TABLE BorderFill="6" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="4" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="3"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2043973746" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" TextWrap="TopAndBottom" ZOrder="15"><SIZE Height="16298" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="42518" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="4197" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="false" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="1084" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="5433" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="8909"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>직 원 명</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="18" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="40"><CHAR>(요양보호사)</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="5433" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="12350"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="18" Sty